{
  "stem": "21482.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They drugged him, put him in a backpack, carried him to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And because we were not searched when we came in-- there was so many people, you know, so many hundred of people walking in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was getting late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was not with me for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I remember just walking with this couple and thinking that they have this little boy, the little boy is there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what are they going to do with him?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as we were going, walking by outside of the ghetto wall, and it was getting dark-- it was already night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it was March, no daylight saving time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was dark already, cold, snowing, miserable weather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the dogs are always barking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The dogs always ready to jump and attack you, tear you to pieces.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Germans always yelling and screaming [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hurry up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we started to hear shooting in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were running, we were already not walking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had to run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were running, made us run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were shooting in the ghetto already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got to the camp, and then we went to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think that that's where my mother was, that I finally found my mother in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really don't remember her walking with me to the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And camp, you know, the barracks were huge and very crowded.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The bunk beds, they were really not like bunk bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were like shelves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't sit on it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to lay down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just the way you see in pictures, that's really the way it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On a level?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were like three to each one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably maybe 35, 40 on walls like this, three tiers high.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
